# Components Structure

Components are organized into several categories:

## Pages

[src/components/pages/](mdc:src/components/pages) contains full page components:

- **test-details**: Test details pages including [results.tsx](mdc:src/components/pages/test-details/results.tsx)
- **question-details**: Question details pages
- **organizer-onboarding**: Onboarding flow for organizers
- **Login pages**: [login-organizer.tsx](mdc:src/components/pages/login-organizer.tsx) and [login-participant.tsx](mdc:src/components/pages/login-participant.tsx)

## UI Components

[src/components/ui/](mdc:src/components/ui) contains reusable UI primitives, mostly built on top of Radix UI.

## Shared Components

[src/components/shared/](mdc:src/components/shared) contains shared components used across multiple pages.

## Magic UI

[src/components/magicui/](mdc:src/components/magicui) contains special UI effects and animations.
